page.content: { Detached, Semi-detached, Terrace There are more people living in terraced homes in Durweston than in semi- and detached homes. Detached 21: Semi- 24: Terrace 34 { { Homes and Buildings We found out that apart from homes there are more workshops than anything else in Durweston. { { Names of Homes } This is a selection of some of the names that the people of Durweston have given to their homes: 'Arden','Chy Lowena','Methody', 'Hardy's','Little Stour', 'Mill House','Conifer Coombe Cottage', 'May Cottage Pottery','Russell House', 'St.Michael's','Shioch's Crafts', 'The Mill'.
